 3.4 英寸外部显示屏，让您可以回复消息、使用钱包和以其他方式处理以前需要打开手机的任务。新的铰链设计还消除了手机关闭时的间隙。您还可以期待更快的定制 Snapdragon 8 Gen 2 芯片和双倍的存储空间。它的起价为 999 美元，可在 8 月 11 日发布之前通过<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=f85e63cd-e13c-4f9d-991c-9fbaadede3ac&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Samsung+Electronics&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiJmODVlNjNjZC1lMTNjLTRmOWQtOTkxYy05ZmJhYWRlZGUzYWMiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2Ftc3VuZy5jb20vdXMvc21hcnRwaG9uZXMvZ2FsYXh5LXotZmxpcDUvYnV5LyIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiZTU3ZGZmZmMtOTgzYy00Y2QzLWIxZDItYjY3OWUzZDFkNDkzIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAUaTVZD_d4tdEPhlJxBhiKY_bmRXuQAAaGDi8Lb0Xijd&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.samsung.com%2Fus%2Fsmartphones%2Fgalaxy-z-flip5%2Fbuy%2F&amp;uuid=q57qwpEUUOtqdynL0663">三星</a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMENDQzJWVFdTLz90YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby0xcmItMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImU1N2RmZmZjLTk4M2MtNGNkMy1iMWQyLWI2NzllM2QxZDQ5MyJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAYpgfr8fV3g50bTnmyuKTYV1FuKxOmGXTKE-czMDU-bu&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0CCC2VTWS%2F&amp;uuid=JPROjjxRwtCgQiAl1664">亚马逊</a>预订。</p><p>与此同时，Galaxy Z Fold 5 是一次<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/samsung-galaxy-z-fold-5-hands-on-specs-price-is-samsung-squandering-its-head-start-110009600.html">迭代（如果仍然受欢迎的话）更新</a>。这款书本式可折叠产品采用更薄、无间隙的设计，具有更明亮的主显示屏、Snapdragon 8 Gen 2 和改进的多任务处理能力。它将于 8 月 11 日发货，起价 1,799 美元，您现在可以通过<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=f85e63cd-e13c-4f9d-991c-9fbaadede3ac&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureI